---
title: "Kaupunginvaltuusto"
metaTitle: "Kaupunginvaltuusto ja poliittinen työ"
description: "Oulun kaupunginvaltuuston kokoukset, joissa Jari Larun puheenvuorot, valtuustoaloitteet ja valtuuston kyselytunnin asiat näkyvät kokouskohtaisesti."
permalink: /politiikka/kaupunginvaltuusto/
layout: base.njk
lang: fi
translationKey: council_meetings
templateEngineOverride: njk
pageShell: true
pageShellClass: site-shell site-shell--wide
pageScopeClass: council-meetings-page-scope
schemaAbout:
  - "@type": "Thing"
    name: "Oulun kaupunginvaltuusto"
    description: "Kokouskohtainen näkymä Jari Larun valtuustopuheenvuoroihin, valtuustoaloitteisiin ja valtuuston kyselytunnin asioihin."
schemaMentions:
  - "@type": "GovernmentOrganization"
    name: "Oulun kaupunki"
    url: "https://www.ouka.fi/"
  - "@type": "Organization"
    name: "Oulun kaupunginvaltuusto"
    url: "https://www.ouka.fi/valtuusto"
---

{% set meetings = councilMeetings %}
{% set timeline = councilMeetingTimeline %}

<section class="council-meetings">
  <header class="council-meetings-hero">
    <div>
      <p class="term-eyebrow mb-2">Poliittinen työ</p>
      <h1 class="term-hero-title mb-3">Kaupunginvaltuusto</h1>
      <p class="term-hero-lead mb-0">Tämä näkymä kokoaa samaan kokoukseen kuuluvat puheenvuorot, valtuustoaloitteet ja valtuuston kyselytunnin asiat. Kokous toimii väliportaana yksittäisten tekstien ja vaalikausien välillä.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="council-meetings-hero-card">
      <p class="term-hero-card__kicker">Kokoussolmu</p>
      <p>Varsinaisissa korteissa näkyvät kokoukseen kytketyt omat sisällöt. Pienet välimaininnat näyttävät kokoukset, joista sivustolla ei ole omaa puheenvuoroa.</p>
      <strong>{{ timeline.length }} kokousta</strong>
    </aside>
  </header>

  <div class="council-meetings-list" aria-label="Kaupunginvaltuuston kokoukset">
    {% for meeting in timeline %}
    {% if meeting.isQuiet %}
    <div class="council-meeting-marker" id="kokous-{{ meeting.date }}">
      <span class="council-meeting-marker__date">{{ meeting.date | dateFormat }}</span>
      <span class="council-meeting-marker__title">{% if meeting.meetingNumber %}Kokous {{ meeting.meetingNumber }}{% else %}{{ meeting.meetingLabel }}{% endif %}</span>
      <span class="council-meeting-marker__note">{% if meeting.timelineKind == "annual-cycle" %}Valtuuston vuosikello{% else %}Ei omaa puheenvuoroa sivustolla{% endif %}</span>
      {% if meeting.video and meeting.video.url %}
      <a href="{{ meeting.video.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kokousvideo</a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <article class="council-meeting-card" id="kokous-{{ meeting.date }}">
      <div class="council-meeting-card__date">
        <span>{{ meeting.date | dateFormat }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="council-meeting-card__body">
        <h2><a href="/politiikka/kaupunginvaltuusto/kokoukset/{{ meeting.date }}/">{{ meeting.meetingLabel }}</a></h2>
        <p class="council-meeting-card__meta">{{ meeting.contextLabel }} · {{ meeting.date | dateFormat }}</p>
        {% if meeting.summaryTitle %}
        <p class="council-meeting-card__summary">{{ meeting.summaryTitle }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="council-meeting-counts" aria-label="Kokouksen sisällöt">
          {% if meeting.counts.speeches %}<span>{{ meeting.counts.speeches }} {{ "puheenvuoro" if meeting.counts.speeches == 1 else "puheenvuoroa" }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% if meeting.counts.questions %}<span>{{ meeting.counts.questions }} {{ "kyselytunnin asia" if meeting.counts.questions == 1 else "kyselytunnin asiaa" }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% if meeting.counts.initiatives %}<span>{{ meeting.counts.initiatives }} {{ "valtuustoaloite" if meeting.counts.initiatives == 1 else "valtuustoaloitetta" }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% if meeting.counts.other %}<span>{{ meeting.counts.other }} {{ "muu sisältö" if meeting.counts.other == 1 else "muuta sisältöä" }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <ul class="council-meeting-preview">
          {% for item in meeting.items %}
          {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
            <span>{{ item.typeLabel }}{% if item.detailLabel %} · {{ item.detailLabel }}{% endif %}</span>
          </li>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="council-meeting-card__actions">
        <a class="btn btn-read-more rounded-pill px-4" href="/politiikka/kaupunginvaltuusto/kokoukset/{{ meeting.date }}/">Avaa kokous</a>
        {% if meeting.protocolUrl %}
        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4" href="{{ meeting.protocolUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pöytäkirja</a>
        {% endif %}
        {% if meeting.video and meeting.video.url %}
        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4" href="{{ meeting.video.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kokousvideo</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.council-meetings {
  display: grid;
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
}

.council-meetings-hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(18rem, 0.85fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: stretch;
  padding: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  border: 1px solid rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.1);
  border-radius: 1.4rem;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(125, 159, 199, 0.16), transparent 34%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(245, 249, 255, 0.92));
  box-shadow: 0 1rem 2.4rem rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.08);
}

.council-meetings-hero-card {
  display: grid;
  align-content: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.1);
  border-radius: 1.2rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.78);
}

.council-meetings-hero-card p {
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.council-meetings-hero-card strong {
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
  line-height: 1;
  color: #102845;
}

.council-meetings-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.65rem;
}

.council-meeting-marker {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.45rem 0.7rem;
  padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
  margin-inline: clamp(0rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
  border: 1px dashed rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.16);
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.44);
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.58);
  font-size: 0.86rem;
}

.council-meeting-marker__date,
.council-meeting-marker__title {
  font-weight: 800;
}

.council-meeting-marker__note {
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.5);
}

.council-meeting-marker a {
  color: rgba(18, 53, 95, 0.72);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration-thickness: 0.08em;
  text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
}

.council-meeting-card {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(9rem, 0.22fr) minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(12rem, 0.26fr);
  gap: 1.25rem;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.1);
  border-radius: 1.25rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
  box-shadow: 0 0.7rem 1.8rem rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.06);
}

.council-meeting-card__date span {
  display: inline-flex;
  padding: 0.48rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.08);
  color: #163e6c;
  font-weight: 800;
}

.council-meeting-card__body h2 {
  margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 0.8vw, 1.85rem);
  line-height: 1.18;
}

.council-meeting-card__meta,
.council-meeting-card__summary {
  margin: -0.35rem 0 0.8rem;
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.68);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.council-meeting-card__summary {
  margin-top: -0.25rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.council-meeting-card__body h2 a,
.council-meeting-preview a {
  color: #12355f;
  text-decoration-thickness: 0.08em;
  text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
}

.council-meeting-counts {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.45rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}

.council-meeting-counts span {
  display: inline-flex;
  padding: 0.32rem 0.65rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.08);
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.8);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.council-meeting-preview {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none;
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.65rem;
}

.council-meeting-preview li {
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.15rem;
}

.council-meeting-preview span {
  color: rgba(17, 40, 70, 0.64);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.council-meeting-card__actions {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  align-items: stretch;
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meetings-hero,
[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-card {
  border-color: rgba(214, 226, 240, 0.18);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(23, 36, 54, 0.96), rgba(17, 27, 42, 0.92));
  box-shadow: none;
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-marker {
  border-color: rgba(214, 226, 240, 0.16);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
  color: rgba(236, 242, 248, 0.58);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-marker__note {
  color: rgba(236, 242, 248, 0.48);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-marker a {
  color: rgba(214, 226, 240, 0.78);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meetings-hero-card {
  border-color: rgba(214, 226, 240, 0.18);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  color: rgba(236, 242, 248, 0.78);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meetings-hero-card strong,
[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-card__body h2 a,
[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-preview a {
  color: #f6fbff;
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-card__meta,
[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-card__summary {
  color: rgba(236, 242, 248, 0.72);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-card__date span,
[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-counts span {
  background: rgba(214, 226, 240, 0.12);
  color: rgba(246, 251, 255, 0.92);
}

[data-bs-theme="dark"] .council-meeting-preview span {
  color: rgba(236, 242, 248, 0.68);
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .council-meetings-hero,
  .council-meeting-card {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .council-meeting-card__actions {
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
}
</style>
